title: Cloudstack virtualrouters
agents: linux
catalog: cloud/cloudstack
distribution: https://github.com/AlexanderStock/cloudstack_nagios
author: Alexander Stock <mail@stock-alexander.de>
license: GPL
description:
    This check is for monitoring the status of virtualrouters connected to cloudstack.
    This means you will see the alert state of a virtualrouters and also if a virtualrouters disconnects unplanned.
    Also the updatestatus and the HA status of redundant VPC setups will be checked.

